== 改善数据结构 ==
查询是可以了,但是,使用默认的列表打印格式来存储和汇报实在不乍的, 想修改就修改
{{{#!python
#cdctools.py...
def formatCDinfo(root,dirs,files):
    export = "\n"+root+"\n"
    for d in dirs:
        export+= "-d "+root+_smartcode(d)+"\n"
    for f in files:
        export+= "-f %s %s \n" % (root,_smartcode(f))
    export+= "="*70
    return export
}}}
